 paradigm offers a direct pathway towards\nmanufacturing phononic metamaterials, DNA origami structures and topolectric\ncircuits that can realize a wide range of static and dynamic target\nfunctionalities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Feb 2018 17:31:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 May 2019 17:34:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
