o-mechanical structures, enabling progresses towards\nthe understanding of intrinsic sources of noise in these devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Feb 2018 17:40:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 08:59:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-11"}
