 the network requires accurate learning of its weights, a property that\ndoes not hold in a more general setting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Feb 2018 19:40:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 21:05:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 10:34:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-11"}
