age the Feynman-Kitaev\nclock construction to approximately embed a subspace of states defined by a\ncircuit as the ground space of a local Hamiltonian.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Feb 2018 04:08:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Mar 2018 18:22:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2019 21:10:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-26"}
